@startuml ReturnBook
' Robustness Diagram: Return Book
' Group: G25 - Library Management System

skinparam monochrome true
title Robustness Diagram: Return Book\nGroup G25 - Library Management System

actor Member
actor Librarian
boundary "Return\nScreen" as ReturnScreen <<Boundary>>
boundary "Scan\nInterface" as ScanUI <<Boundary>>
control "Return\nController" as ReturnCtrl <<Control>>
control "Date\nValidator" as DateValidator <<Control>>
entity "Book" as Book <<Entity>>
entity "Loan\nRecord" as LoanRecord <<Entity>>

Member --> ReturnScreen : 1. Initiate
Librarian --> ScanUI : 1. Process
ReturnScreen --> ReturnCtrl : 2. Submit
ScanUI --> DateValidator : 3. Scan
ReturnCtrl --> Book : 4. Update
DateValidator --> LoanRecord : 5. Close

note bottom: * Extends to Pay Fine if overdue

@enduml
